Package se350.elevatorSim.elevator

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Elevator
    An Elevator interface that defines behavior for every elevator implementation.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ElevatorDTO
    Class that holds data so the ElevatorController can give the status of each Elevator instance to its delegates to choose which one to give a request to.
    ElevatorFactory
    Factory that creates Elevator implementations that best fit the parameters.
    ElevatorImpl
    An implementation of the Elevator interface that creates a simple elevator.
    ElevatorImplTest  
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Elevator.Status
    Enum that defines the different states that an Elevator instance can be in depending on it's current action.
